{"id":232889686,"title":"蝦皮會自動連接通訊錄的任何人嗎？","content":"想請問有沒有人知道這個問題嗎😫\n爬文都沒有相關答案，之前看過迪卡一篇是已經開啟隱私設定了但朋友那邊的通訊錄還是看得到她在使用的蝦皮帳號。\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/74cc6cb8-b1f9-4b21-a7f4-fc7bd9d9df49/1280.jpeg\n就是蝦皮的設定頁面那裡可以更改，而且其實我不知道初始設定是什麼？如果初始設定是關閉的那其實也來不及了等於ㄧ辦好蝦皮帳號就會自動通知所有通訊錄聯絡人（包括老師、爸爸、媽媽....@@）\n\n想請問有人知道就算開啟這個不讓通訊錄的人知道我在使用蝦皮的設定，他們那邊到底還會不會接收到「某某某有在使用蝦皮喔可以關注他➕」的訊息之類的？\n\n覺得蝦皮的隱私部分做的真的很差，我想應該不是每個人都想要自己使用蝦皮買賣東西被通訊錄所有人都知道吧0.0","excerpt":"想請問有沒有人知道這個問題嗎，爬文都沒有相關答案，之前看過迪卡一篇是已經開啟隱私設定了但朋友那邊的通訊錄還是看得到她在使用的蝦皮帳號。就是蝦皮的設定頁面那裡可以更改，而且其實我不知道初始設定是什麼？如","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d5ee9d02-510e-4f81-96e9-ab59b56e21ca","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-14T10:23:36.583Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T10:25:23.692Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["蝦皮","隱私","通訊錄"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"網路購物","forumAlias":"buyonline","school":"實踐大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/74cc6cb8-b1f9-4b21-a7f4-fc7bd9d9df49/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9ac08a15-5f7f-4f3a-9a20-53d1885a0c1f","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/74cc6cb8-b1f9-4b21-a7f4-fc7bd9d9df49/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/74cc6cb8-b1f9-4b21-a7f4-fc7bd9d9df49/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/74cc6cb8-b1f9-4b21-a7f4-fc7bd9d9df49/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-14T10:23:36.583Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-14T10:25:23.692Z","width":296,"height":640},{"id":"9ac08a15-5f7f-4f3a-9a20-53d1885a0c1f","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/74cc6cb8-b1f9-4b21-a7f4-fc7bd9d9df4